{"tid":902692,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"HKBN 香港寬頻呃錢勁無恥，入嚟睇下你有冇中招","createTime":"2018-11-15T04:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T09:27:58.000Z","uid":19795,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46975b713da4a916792a8985116b3690f834c158","tid":902692,"uid":19795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港寬頻 HKBN 擅自升級客戶 myTV SUPER 至尊版</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無論你用緊 100M / 200M / 500M / 1000M 香港寬頻<br />\n記得 check 返過去嘅 statement<br />\n睇下入面有冇呢項收費：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">myTV SUPER⾄尊版及新增1個跨屏幕同時睇 2018/xx/xx - 2018/xx/xx $98.00</span></span><br />\n<br />\n上網睇翻，原來佢地呃客有好多種手法，其中包括：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 訛稱打電話得到客戶同意升級<br />\n2. 呃官戶免費升級<br />\n3. 借藉口升級 myTV 帳戶<br />\n4. 打電話核對帳戶資料</span></strong>等等，都有機會俾佢地暗中做手腳而收取額外收費<br />\n<br />\n案例如下： <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/11/15/XnDFxy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F11%2F15%2FXnDFxy.png&h=9ee20901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>如果你未曾主動/同意申請升級，又有呢項收費，證明你就已經瀨咗嘢<br />\n只好係到祝你盡快成功搞得掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span>"},{"pid":"90ee34bf1d9d103cb086170f2ab016124dacbd19","tid":902692,"uid":177411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d13c284377a0a9c6e6e5a80c5eb10bb28056f55","tid":902692,"uid":19795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90ee34bf1d9d103cb086170f2ab016124dacbd19","tid":902692,"uid":177411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T04:13:38.000Z","msg":"咁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201